I just met the same issue **(2)** but about using **tf.train.batch_join()** of the TF' version(0.11.0rc1).  As _**oliverfunk**_ said, i put a comma at the end of the tuple and seems work. 

Thanks!

My code is like as below:     

example_list  = [ \
        **(** img_preprocess.read_my_file_format(                  \
        filename_queue,                                                              \
        reader = tf.WholeFileReader(),                                        \
        decoder= img_preprocess.my_file_decoder_png,         \
        shape  = shape,                                                               \
        isWithLabel= False  **), )** for _ in range(read_threads) ];
